name: Da Varanda #009
description: This is the ninth photo, size 3008 x 2000 px - ISO 400 | 300mm | f/4,0 | 1/6400 sec. One week, an apartment balcony and a camera. This series of photos is being produced from the balcony of my apartment. For 1 week, I will photograph the life that I can see from up here on the 10th floor. All will be minted in 100 editions at a low price and after the sale period, those that are not sold will be burned.
